{"tid":2000473,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"IPHONE入咗DFU Mode 仲有冇方法做Backup？","createTime":"2020-05-04T01:31:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-04T10:54:00.000Z","uid":17099,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"f04c991aa4c0790340b66cd6ef81ee960b3be0b5","tid":2000473,"uid":17099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T01:31:58.000Z","msg":"自己衰On9無空間未Backup就關機<br />\n依家機又開唔到又Update Error 14，一直都係DFU Mode<br />\n只求救返啲貓咪相<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EE31vj5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEE31vj5.jpg&h=4562dc28&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7704bdba506dc181bb36eb25e7eb13e073d62fcb","tid":2000473,"uid":32577,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T01:50:36.000Z","msg":"為左慳8蚊，咁就冇左一堆相。值得咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nbtw 呀寶好忙"},{"pid":"09d7e592302c5361d7ce80c2d1827c4f93b91dc1","tid":2000473,"uid":219147,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T01:57:47.000Z","msg":"開唔到機 唔等如一定開唔到<br />\n試下插住充電同佢加下電壓 <br />\n可能會著得返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ed807fa6d792b5dd3d1f04de3593f6a0302d9ef","tid":2000473,"uid":99642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T01:59:08.000Z","msg":"首先，我們很遺憾地告訴你，由於你的iPhone處於回復模式，你將無法再備份你的iPhone，但是如果你可以在不回復iPhone的情況下使你的iPhone脫離回復模式，你將不會丟失任何資料。"},{"pid":"562e0a95bd463aec45ef92a26efa04a5a4a0fc4d","tid":2000473,"uid":99642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T02:00:39.000Z","msg":"1.3. 退出iPhone回復模式的常用步驟<br />\n<br />\n有時你會發現你的iPhone會卡在回復模式中。現在，如果你想知道有什麼可能的步驟可以幫助你走出困境，回復手機的正常工作，這裏是在正常情況下退出回復模式的步驟。<br />\n<br />\n按住Home鍵和電源鍵約15秒，這將關閉iPhone。<br />\n一直按住啟動按鈕來啟動iPhone。這將使你的iPhone退出回復模式。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n注意：如果你用的是iPhone 7，按下音量鍵而不是主鍵。如果你使用的是iPhone 8或更高版本，快速按音量調高鍵，然後按音量調低鍵，然後按住電源鍵，直到iPhone重啟。"},{"pid":"1b96472176024eb09a15aa01a6673279f685d215","tid":2000473,"uid":17099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7704bdba506dc181bb36eb25e7eb13e073d62fcb","tid":2000473,"uid":32577,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T01:50:36.000Z","msg":"為左慳8蚊，咁就冇左一堆相。值得咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nbtw 呀寶好忙"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T02:01:10.000Z","msg":"知錯了想死 刪刪下相無反應咪試下重開機 點知出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a2aa84a33c33f4669c177b3d8308578efbb91d9","tid":2000473,"uid":17099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"09d7e592302c5361d7ce80c2d1827c4f93b91dc1","tid":2000473,"uid":219147,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T01:57:47.000Z","msg":"開唔到機 唔等如一定開唔到<br />\n試下插住充電同佢加下電壓 <br />\n可能會著得返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T02:04:46.000Z","msg":"插住線了<br />\n依家畫面長期都係有條線對住部電腦 做唔到野<br />\n係咪recovery mode定DFU mode..."},{"pid":"16b7b162ee4792ce5292ce0ef19073a29ba8912a","tid":2000473,"uid":17099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"562e0a95bd463aec45ef92a26efa04a5a4a0fc4d","tid":2000473,"uid":99642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T02:00:39.000Z","msg":"1.3. 退出iPhone回復模式的常用步驟<br />\n<br />\n有時你會發現你的iPhone會卡在回復模式中。現在，如果你想知道有什麼可能的步驟可以幫助你走出困境，回復手機的正常工作，這裏是在正常情況下退出回復模式的步驟。<br />\n<br />\n按住Home鍵和電源鍵約15秒，這將關閉iPhone。<br />\n一直按住啟動按鈕來啟動iPhone。這將使你的iPhone退出回復模式。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n注意：如果你用的是iPhone 7，按下音量鍵而不是主鍵。如果你使用的是iPhone 8或更高版本，快速按音量調高鍵，然後按音量調低鍵，然後按住電源鍵，直到iPhone重啟。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T02:05:39.000Z","msg":"試咗了 出唔到去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5096ad7a447e3e6551fa0b0b6e1d6951e7b31893","tid":2000473,"uid":99642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"16b7b162ee4792ce5292ce0ef19073a29ba8912a","tid":2000473,"uid":17099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"562e0a95bd463aec45ef92a26efa04a5a4a0fc4d","tid":2000473,"uid":99642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T02:00:39.000Z","msg":"1.3. 退出iPhone回復模式的常用步驟<br />\n<br />\n有時你會發現你的iPhone會卡在回復模式中。現在，如果你想知道有什麼可能的步驟可以幫助你走出困境，回復手機的正常工作，這裏是在正常情況下退出回復模式的步驟。<br />\n<br />\n按住Home鍵和電源鍵約15秒，這將關閉iPhone。<br />\n一直按住啟動按鈕來啟動iPhone。這將使你的iPhone退出回復模式。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n注意：如果你用的是iPhone 7，按下音量鍵而不是主鍵。如果你使用的是iPhone 8或更高版本，快速按音量調高鍵，然後按音量調低鍵，然後按住電源鍵，直到iPhone重啟。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T02:05:39.000Z","msg":"試咗了 出唔到去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T02:06:18.000Z","msg":"無back up?<br />\nGG"},{"pid":"44d7dabeb6a816137f3cfbc0636574c76b36ef4b","tid":2000473,"uid":219147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1a2aa84a33c33f4669c177b3d8308578efbb91d9","tid":2000473,"uid":17099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"09d7e592302c5361d7ce80c2d1827c4f93b91dc1","tid":2000473,"uid":219147,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T01:57:47.000Z","msg":"開唔到機 唔等如一定開唔到<br />\n試下插住充電同佢加下電壓 <br />\n可能會著得返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T02:04:46.000Z","msg":"插住線了<br />\n依家畫面長期都係有條線對住部電腦 做唔到野<br />\n係咪recovery mode定DFU mode..."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T02:07:44.000Z","msg":"更係Recovery<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5665316f57b6d0f62318b8c016cf7f493b062a8d","tid":2000473,"uid":17099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"44d7dabeb6a816137f3cfbc0636574c76b36ef4b","tid":2000473,"uid":219147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1a2aa84a33c33f4669c177b3d8308578efbb91d9","tid":2000473,"uid":17099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"09d7e592302c5361d7ce80c2d1827c4f93b91dc1","tid":2000473,"uid":219147,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T01:57:47.000Z","msg":"開唔